                        <locus from="1">(fol. 1)</locus>
                        <author key="person_4136834">William de Montibus</author>
                        <title key="work_5040">Distinctiones theologicae</title>
                        <rubric>Incipit Distinciones W. de Mont. secundum alphabetum</rubric>
                       <incipit>Arcus dicitur Christus &amp; propiciatio Dei</incipit>
                       <note>Short discourses on religious and moral subjects, in alphabetical order of the first word. The first three
                          articles are <hi rend="italic">Arcus</hi>, <hi rend="italic">Adversarius</hi>, <hi rend="italic">Asperges me</hi>; the last are <hi rend="italic">Vota</hi>, <hi rend="italic">Zebus</hi> and <hi rend="italic">Zona</hi></note>
